name: AW CompuTech
overview:
AW CompuTech is able to supply a range of ICT professional services to individuals and businesses.

Web Design - AW CompuTech can provide a web solution to fit customer’s needs ranging from a simple holding page all the way through to a fully featured web application.

Software Engineering - AW CompuTech can provide help in providing software based solutions for customer’s needs. They can fully design and develop software to your requirements, whether this is an add in for a spreadsheet or a full customised application. In addition AW CompuTech can work with any existing code or together with any development team the client may have. Work can be undertaken in C++, VB, VBA and PHP.

Support - AW CompuTech can provide general IT support and consultancy on IT and network facilities. They can advise you on a network design to client’s requirements. We will produce the design and recommend the hardware. Additionally any required software can be installed. General support arrangement covering any IT needs can be arranged.

Backup - AW CompuTech can provide a secure backup system that can either be automated or run manually.
